n of acute and chronic illness）</li>		<li>慢性疾病与管理（managing chronic health conditions）</li>		<li>儿童与青少年健康问题（child &amp; adolescent health）</li>		<li>心理神经<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/免疫学' target='_blank'>免疫学</a>（psychoneuroimmunology）</li>		<li>应对反应与社会支持（coping responses and social support）</li>		<li>疼痛与疼痛管理（pain and pain management）</li>		<li>姑息治疗与临终关怀（palliative and end-of-life care）&nbsp;</li>	</ul>	</li>	<li>社会与文化<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/心理学' target='_blank'>心理学</a>（Social and Cultural Psychology）	<ul>		<li>青年、消费与认同（youth, consumption and identity）</li>		<li>身份、性别与身体形象（identities, gender and body image）</li>		<li>组织<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/心理学' target='_blank'>心理学</a>与风险管理（organisational psychology and the management of risk）</li>		<li>态度与行为（attitude-behaviour relations）</li>		<li>行为与心理习惯（behavioural and mental habits）</li>		<li>情绪调节（emotion regulation）</li>		<li><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/经济学' target='_blank'>经济学</a>与环境<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/心理学' target='_blank'>心理学</a>（economic and environmental psychology）</li>		<li>网络空间与个人关系（personal relationships in cyberspace）</li>		<li>兄弟姐妹与主观性（siblings and subjectivities）</li>		<li>身份与教育（identities and education）*(11)</li>	</ul>	</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=0rRNYshkwhmWQkew14AxzXOkBvTjmfcf5ovMvJtqfhC7zqEQ91eTIYbWrsOG_CySX8y172ISb04-FSqh320I9FSqrK7RI3O2RcpNthKFuXrJ7Rg1f5QIXOyUxBOuM_Ht' target='_blank'>English Language Requirements</a> University of Bath</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ZrygfZwOwp7Hoc0OKKKKK-biSJruZ2dOqVMeMeOhx0h3tNjADeiBGtEBHIuz78vIuXpVVqx_4_dYgBCA7Kt8wB7wFqvSWoUqFMv4L3hfBtJl_FYZm-YdWgHsQl0woMBh4p' target='_blank'>Faculty of Humanities and Social Sciences: Tuition Fees</a> University of Bath</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=JrvWrUMww36DmOescccccgik-IyvSFdfjqjqGopzLIFfr40fZEWfjDyq7IofjgZfwODNhxCHPaSVhU0o1LMahUSVRLMVPo8OKabNGz3j-FD_XLSthBHqaBhtK8-' tar